videos.headline: UAB quarterback lets it fly for 49-yard TD
videos.description: Tyler Johnston III puts it up in the air to Kendall Parham who catches it while sprinting to the end zone for a 49-yard touchdown in the first quarter vs. Akron.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UAB quarterback lets it fly for 49-yard TD) 2019/9/7 ESHEET

videos.headline: UAB scores improbable TD on third down
videos.description: Tyler Johnston III braces for the hit while getting the throw off to Austin Watkins, who makes a catch just inches from the end zone and he's swung in for the score by Akron defenders.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UAB scores improbable TD on third down) 2019/9/7 ESHEET

videos.headline: Johnston goes deep to Mitchell for 76-yard TD
videos.description: For his fourth touchdown on the day, Tyler Johnston III throws a long pass to Myron Mitchell for a 76-yard touchdown in UAB's 31-20 win over Akron.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Johnston goes deep to Mitchell for 76-yard TD) 2019/9/7 ESHEET
